  "description": "A powerful ocean wave is captured mid-break, cresting and curling with significant force. The wave is a mix of deep blues and bright whites as it rolls forward. The crest of the wave is frothy and turbulent, filled with white foam and spray. There's a sense of dynamic energy and movement as the water collapses in on itself. The lighting is natural and highlights the textures of the water and foam.",
